             were indicted for <rs id="t17820911-58-off303" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17820911-58-off303" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820911-58-off303" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17820911-58-victim683" type="victimName">
                           Elizabeth 
                           Jacobs
                        <interp inst="t17820911-58-victim683" type="surname" value="Jacobs"></interp>
